snippet.title: What Lies in the Multiverse - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
✅ Link to the game 👉  https://bit.ly/3tziyuS

What Lies in the Multiverse is a story-driven puzzle platformer filled to the brim with hijinks, chaos, and reality-bending adventure. Harness the power of the multiverse! Switch worlds in mid-air, turning pitfalls into bridges, walls into tunnels, and foes into friends. Just be careful when you mess around with gravity…
